id: Defines the key: String with alphanumeric char + '_'. One occurence of '.' is authoriorised
analytic_account_id/id:
Many2one field type: Autorised value: 'module_name.key' defined on the file account.analytic.account.csv

                                As exemple import_data.product1 The field is required
employee_id/id:
Many2one field type: Autorised value: 'module_name.key' defined on the file hr.employee.csv

                                As exemple import_data.product1 The field is not required
sequence: Intedger field type: Autorised value: XXXXX as exemple: 125 Please note that the number is without ',' or '.' The field is not required
period_date_stop: Date field type: Autorised value: AAAA-MM-DD as exemple: 2012-05-28 The field is not required
solucom_type: Char field type: Autorised value: a string with 16 as max size The field is not required
period_days_number: Intedger field type: Autorised value: XXXXX as exemple: 125 Please note that the number is without ',' or '.' The field is not required
delete_property: Boolean field: Autorised value: "True" or "False".  The field is not required
analytic_period_id/id:
Many2one field type: Autorised value: 'module_name.key' defined on the file account.analytic.period.csv

                                As exemple import_data.product1 The field is not required
write_date: Datetime field type: Autorised value: AAAA-MM-DD HH:MM:SS as exemple: 2012-05-28 12:30:SS The field is not required
timesheet_id/id:
Many2one field type: Autorised value: 'module_name.key' defined on the file timesheet.timesheet.csv

                                As exemple import_data.product1 The field is required
period_date_start: Date field type: Autorised value: AAAA-MM-DD as exemple: 2012-05-28 The field is not required
total: Float field type: Autorised value: XXXXX.DD as exemple: 125.01 Please note that the digit separator is '.' The field is not required
input_chain: Text field type: Autorised value: Text The field is required
display_property: Char field type: Autorised value: a string with 32 as max size The field is not required
